  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this multi-center prospective study is to evaluate the diagnostic performance
      of S-Shearwave, a newly developed ultrasound shear wave elastography, for the assessment of
      hepatic fibrosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
