  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with chronic liver disease or cirrhosis, or living-donor candidates for liver
             transplantation, or volunteers

          -  Signed informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Acute hepatitis or bile duct obstruction

          -  Serum ALT&gt; 5 times the upper limit of normal within 3 months

          -  s/p Rt. hemihepatectomy

          -  s/p liver transplantation

          -  Large mass or infiltrative lesion in the right lobe of the liver
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
